Package: MarkovThiele
Type: Package
Title: The package allows the user to construct and evalute markov chains
Version: 0.3.0
Author: Markus Ausserhofer
Description: The package defines a Markov-Thiele-chain-S3-object, offers functions to construct and evaluate such objects.
    The user can compute the present value of expected cashflows as well as the distribution of future cashflows.
